    "testimonials_mUYTyV": {
      "type": "testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "testimonial_YFmRqt": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>The new Mars 3.0 features a fully reworked frame with an internally housed battery and a Horst-link suspension system—something you almost never see on a folding e-bike.</p>",
            "author": "",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Electric.jpg",
            "image_ratio": "adapt",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_aenwVm": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>With real power, actual suspension, and smart features that make it more refined and useful, this is a folding e-bike that doesn’t ride like a compromise.</p>",
            "author": "",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/electrek_1.jpg",
            "image_ratio": "adapt",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_kxb6Lh": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>So while you can go mountain biking with the Hero, you’ll be best served keeping the pace reasonable.</p>",
            "author": "",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Forbes.jpg",
            "image_ratio": "adapt",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_AnUCGK": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>Even at the fifth and highest level of pedal assist, the Alpha is smooth and easy to control, making you feel like you’re pedaling a traditional push bike. There’s nothing jerky about the acceleration.</p>",
            "author": "",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/tech.jpg",
            "image_ratio": "adapt",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        }
